123
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:51,070
<i>Se zástupcem velite, Choi Ahn-Kangem,
 z velitelství.</i>

124
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,490
<i>Ano, znám ho.</i>

125
00:13:54,700 --> 00:14:00,200
